## **Level Objective**

The goal of this level is for you to log into the game using SSH. The host to which you need to connect is bandit.labs.overthewire.org, on port 2220. The username is bandit0 and the password is bandit0. Once logged in, go to the Level 1 page to find out how to beat Level 1.

## **Commands Needed**

`ssh`: A command-line tool to securely connect to remote systems.

## **Solution**

Step 1:
- Connect to the server using the `ssh` command. The general syntax looks like this `ssh user@host -p port number`

Step 2
-  Once you fill in the host(Bandit and the level you're on) and the host (bandit.labs.overthewire.org) with port number 2220. You will be prompted to fill in the password.

Step 3
- The password for this level is bandit0. Once done click enter and you will be connected to the bandit server

## **Resources**

- [SSH - Secure Shell on Wikipedia](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Secure_Shell)
- [How to use SSH on wikiHow](https://www.wikihow.com/Use-SSH)

